title: Triallion Perfect World - 1.3.6 Private Server
description:
Triallion is a Perfect World Private Server with a twist, come join us on a new adventure, taking part in our new storyline quests filled with mystery and questions. Discover how the story ends and learn where it began. Will you be the one to discover who? What? Or where? the Legendary Centuria is? All we know for sure is that this force has unleashed many new creatures upon our world to ravage the unsuspecting and bring fear to even the most hardened hearts.
